Package: rpt
Type: Package
Title: R Package Template
Version: 1.2.1
Date: 2018-12-31
Authors@R: c(
    person("Boris", "Steipe", email = "boris.steipe@utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1134-6758"))
    )
Description: A template for an RStudio project of a basic R package with a
             GitHub repository. rpt follows principles described in
             Hadley Wickham's R Packages book and is compatible with CRAN
             guidelines. The project is version controlled, contains testing
             code, can be installed from GitHub using standard tools, and 
             includes extensive instructions on how to install and customize.
